@startuml
title Hospital Management System - Activity Diagram with Swimlanes

|Patient|
start
:Register Account;
:Book appointment;

|Hospital Management System|
:Validate patient information;
:Check doctor availability;
:Create appointment record;

|Notification Service|
:Send appointment confirmation;

|Doctor|
:View appointment schedule;
:Open patient medical history;
:Examine patient;
:Enter diagnosis;

if (Tests required?) then (Yes)

  |Doctor|
  :Request diagnostic test;

  |Hospital Management System|
  :Send test request to department;

  |Laboratory / Radiology Staff|
  :Perform requested diagnostic test;
  :Upload diagnostic result;

  |Hospital Management System|
  :Attach diagnostic results\nto patient medical record;

  |Doctor|
  :Review diagnostic results;

else (No)
  |Doctor|
  :Continue without diagnostic tests;
endif

|Doctor|
:Write prescription;
:Update medical record;

|Pharmacist|
:View prescription;
:Dispense medication;

|Billing Officer|
:Generate invoice;
:Record payment status;

|Patient|
:View medical report;
:View billing details;

stop
@enduml